  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink266-kilavi">notumalar varaivu piṟantuḻit talaimakaṭk uḷatākiya vēṟupāṭu tōḻi kūṟit talaimakaṉai varaivukaṭāyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">How the confidante incited the hero to marriage, speaking of the change that came upon the heroine when the prospect of marriage with strangers arose.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink266">
<l>ciṟukaṭ paṉṟip peruñciṉa voruttaloṭu</l>
<l>kuṟukkai yirumpuli porūu nāṭa</l>
<l>naṉinā ṇuṭaimaiya maṉṟa</l>
<l>paṉippayan taṉanī nayantōḷ kaṇṇē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where</l>
        <l>the dark tiger with short legs combats with</l>
        <l>the very angry male of the small-eyed pig,</l>
        <l rend="space">the eyes of she whom you longed for,</l>
        <l> which have produced tears,</l>
        <l>possess much shame.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
